{"tid":2516344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"觀塘男警執勤 遺失警察手提電話","createTime":"2021-05-04T14:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T14:44:52.000Z","uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f80f734e75f83150c8b866462973c91051c677a8","tid":2516344,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:41:24.000Z","msg":"一名隸屬觀塘警區的男警，昨日（3日）下午在觀塘執勤期間，意外遺失一部警察手提電話。警方接獲報告後已立即調查，並在可能遺失地點搜尋，暫未發現。案件列作「遺失政府財物」，由觀塘警區跟進調查。該部警察手提電話隨即被終止服務及已失效，電話內的資料已被移除。警方呼籲市民如拾獲該部手提電話，應立即交到就近的警署，或致電3661 0511與觀塘警署人員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210504/5Z6GMMEJGVFPPG2YKRKQAGXNXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210504%2F5Z6GMMEJGVFPPG2YKRKQAGXNXM%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=26cb2786\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210504%2F5Z6GMMEJGVFPPG2YKRKQAGXNXM%2F&h=623adadc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210504/5Z6GMMEJGVFPPG2YKRKQAGXNXM/</a>"},{"pid":"d90ded57c2c76cfdda8b15234d639bd55071f3f1","tid":2516344,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"咁快就唔見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a81b74712187014deb712c5e5fc2ca70fb459c","tid":2516344,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"跌咗個腦先做到差佬"},{"pid":"4b5d8a3fbdcf237d73ab20fa855196d32e417453","tid":2516344,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"有無市民身份證紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f719f795b093321f4f3b8bb115054e5685a55b8c","tid":2516344,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d90ded57c2c76cfdda8b15234d639bd55071f3f1","tid":2516344,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14